            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "So, after revisiting this, it seems that my mistake was to explicitly use the Cython `build_ext` class at all. Thanks to the convoluted maze of conditional imports both in Setuptools' and Cython's `build_ext`, the regular (Setuptools) `build_ext` class winds up deriving from the Cython one and does all the right things. So the solution is to simply drop the `cmdclass` option.",
